title: EYL #159: EYL’s Live Podcast from Egypt (Business in Africa)
itunes:title: EYL #159: EYL’s Live Podcast from Egypt (Business in Africa)
description:
We did a live podcast/networking event at sunset, on the top of the Nile River Ritz Carlton. We were overlooking The Nile River, Cairo, and The Giza Pyramids. A group of Earners from America and Egypt were in attendance. We interviewed one of the top fintech entrepreneurs in Egypt, Mohammed Aboulnaga Nagaty.


We talked about international markets, banking apps, startups, crypto, gold, The Metaverse, business creation, business in Africa and more. #Egypt #business #internationalbusiness 


EYL University: https://www.eyluniversity.com


Host IG: https://instagram.com/earnyourleisure?utm_medium=copy_link


Guest IG: https: https://instagram.com/nagaty?utm_medium=copy_link


Market Mondays Live Show & Workshop: https://www.marketmondays.com/

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
